title: I didn't receive Victorious Graves!?!?!
body: I didn't receive Victorious Graves and the plat icon. {{sticker:cass-cry}}

replies.body: Heya, we're still distributing rewards!  There are a lot of players, just hang tight.  We'll also have updates on the [service status](http://status.leagueoflegends.com/#na) page.

Hey. I haven't received the victorious graves nor my gold icon. I was banned for 14 days but that ended a couple weeks ago so it shouldn't be a problem right? I read somewhere that you won't get it only if you have an ongoing ban but i might be wrong.
I would file a ticket with Riot Support and include screenshots of your rank as proof if you havent already
